# Vocabulary Content Map

Vocabulary browsing organised by word type and semantic category.

## Route Structure

```
/learn/vocabulary/:tab
/learn/vocabulary/verbs/:verbId  (detail page)
```

Tabs: nouns, verbs, reference
Note: "phrases" tab redirects to /learn/phrases

## Data Source

DB queries via `getVocabularyData()` in `data.server.ts`:
- `getVocabBySection("nouns")` - Noun categories
- `getVocabBySection("verbs")` - Verb-related content
- `getVocabBySection("reference")` - Numbers, colours, adverbs
- `getVerbsWithPatterns()` - Verbs with conjugation family info

